and then splitting like that.

431
00:49:50,554 --> 00:49:52,886
I'm so angry at her.

432
00:49:52,923 --> 00:49:55,187
She seemed
a little upset herself.

433
00:49:55,225 --> 00:49:56,749
I'd like to strangle her.

434
00:49:56,793 --> 00:49:59,353
