In front of the kiosk.

518
00:55:03,633 --> 00:55:05,430
-You've got it.
-Thanks, Joy.

519
00:55:05,468 --> 00:55:06,992
No problem. Thanks.

520
00:55:30,727 --> 00:55:33,025
Hello,
this is the Greer residence.

521
00:55:33,063 --> 00:55:35,623
